Data collection began in 1933, but data are presented here from 1946 onwards. The data were initially collected by the Freshwater Biological Association (FBA), then by CEH and its predecessor Institute of Freshwater Ecology (IFE) from 1989 to 2003, and subsequently again by FBA.     </dcterms:description>     <dcterms:creator>clamw</dcterms:creator>     <documentcontainer:catalogLink>http://data.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/453fdf49-7328-42ec-94b7-1cebf06c51e2</documentcontainer:catalogLink>     <documentcontainer:fileIdentifier xml:lang="en">453fdf49-7328-42ec-94b7-1cebf06c51e2</documentcontainer:fileIdentifier>     <dcterms:subject>monthly</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>lake</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>water</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Environmental monitoring facilities</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>Lake District</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>CEH Water Programme</dcterms:subject>     <dcterms:subject>NERC_DDC</dcterms:subject>     <documentcontainer:id xml:lang="en">453fdf49-7328-42ec-94b7-1cebf06c51e2</documentcontainer:id>     <dcterms:hasPart>       <file:File rdf:about="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/453fdf49-7328-42ec-94b7-1cebf06c51e2/windermere-monthly-temperatures-1946-2012-dataset-documentation">         <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2014-08-11T14:30:05Z</dcterms:created>         <dcterms:modified rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2014-08-11T14:30:06Z</dcterms:modified>         <dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="http://eidchub.ceh.ac.uk/metadata/453fdf49-7328-42ec-94b7-1cebf06c51e2"/>         <dcterms:title xml:lang="en">Windermere monthly temperatures 1946-2012 Dataset Documentation</dcterms:title>         <file:id xml:lang="en">windermere-monthly-temperatures-1946-2012-dataset-documentation</file:id>         <dcterms:creator>clamw</dcterms:creator>       </file:File>     </dcterms:hasPart>   </documentcontainer:documentContainer> </rdf:RDF>
